issues.body:
**Bug description**
The class IAMAuthenticator (inside WatsonxAiApi) did not use the baseUrl.
Inside IamAuthenticator is the url "https://iam.cloud.ibm.com" hard coded.  

**Environment**
Spring AI version: 1.0.0-SNAPSHOT
Java version: 21.0.5

**Steps to reproduce**
By using the configuration (see below) application.yml and the Restcontroller (see below) i got the error:
2025-04-14T07:54:10.816+02:00 ERROR 12084 --- [nio-8080-exec-1] o.a.c.c.C.[.[.[/].[dispatcherServlet]    : Servlet.service() for servlet [dispatcherServlet] in context with
path [] threw exception [Request processing failed: org.springframework.ai.retry.NonTransientAiException: 401 - {"errors":[{"code":"authentication_token_not_valid","message"
:"Failed to authenticate the request due to invalid token: Failed to parse and verify token","more_info":"https://cloud.ibm.com/apidocs/watsonx-ai-cp"}],"trace":"407d5bf3-81
8d-4bdf-afd9-cf90a9b521aa","status_code":401}] with root cause

org.springframework.ai.retry.NonTransientAiException: 401 - {"errors":[{"code":"authentication_token_not_valid","message":"Failed to authenticate the request due to invalid
token: Failed to parse and verify token","more_info":"https://cloud.ibm.com/apidocs/watsonx-ai-cp"}],"trace":"407d5bf3-818d-4bdf-afd9-cf90a9b521aa","status_code":401}

The reason for this error is the system used the hard coded url "https://iam.cloud.ibm.com" instead of the baseUrl "https://brimborium.entw.de"

**Expected behavior**
IamAuthenticator is using the baseUrl from config spring.ai.watsonx.ai.base-url

**Minimal Complete Reproducible example**
application.yml
spring:
  ai:
    model.chat: watsonx
    watsonx:
      ai:
        base-url: https://brimborium.entw.de
        text-endpoint: "ml/v1/text/generation?version=2023-05-29"
        project-id: ***
        iam-token: ***
        chat:
          options:
            model: ibm/granite-3-8b-instruct
            decoding-method: "greedy"

@RestController
public class WatsonxController {

    private final WatsonxAiChatModel chatModel;

	public WatsonxController(WatsonxAiChatModel chatModel) {
                this.chatModel = chatModel;

		System.setProperty("https.proxyHost", "myproxy.localnet.de");
		System.setProperty("https.proxyPort", "3128");
		System.setProperty("http.nonProxyHosts", "localhost");
	}

	@GetMapping("/chat")
	public ResponseEntity<String> chat(@RequestParam Question question) {

        WatsonxAiChatOptions options = WatsonxAiChatOptions.builder()
            .decodingMethod("sample") // greedy
			.maxNewTokens(500)
			.minNewTokens(1)
			.repetitionPenalty(1.05)
            .build();

		Prompt prompt = new Prompt(new UserMessage(question.toString()), options);

		System.out.println("prompt: " + prompt.toString());

        var results = chatModel.call(prompt);

        ChatAnswer chatAnswer = ChatAnswer.of(results.getResult().getOutput().getText());

		return ResponseEntity.ok(chatAnswer.toString());
	}

}
